                  </div>
                </td>
                <td class="td-name">Fancy Type</td>
                <td class="td-desc">
                  <p>Gives you classes to use if you'd like some extra fancy typography.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3"><h3>CATEGORY:</h3></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="even">
